We are Looking for:

An experienced iOS developer to join our Mobile Team.

The Project:

You will be involved in developing a custom mobile project for our client in Germany using the latest mobile technologies (iOS). Among the features of the app are: communication with electric bike (ebike), synchronization with the online, high quality design, in-app billing, security.
Our partner is a leading provider of digital solutions for the consumer goods market, based in the USA. 

Responsibilities:

* To contribute to the continuous enhancement of the mCommerce platform, working with interesting mobile development technologies and leveraging the latest user experience approaches
* Actively participating in agile development teams

Requirements:

* 3+ years experience in a software development position
* Experience with iOS SDK (at least 3 years)
* Very good knowledge of OOP & design patterns
* Very good knowledge of coding best practices
* Experience with Multi-Threading and Concurrency
* Git work experienceLeadership potential
* Good English skills are required

Nice to have:

* Experience with: Bluetooth APIs, iOS 8, Unit Testing 
* Know-how or experience with other mobile technologies such as Android, Windows Phone or BlackBerry

We Value:

* Respect
* Reliability
* Strive for excellence

Notes:

# Only candidates selected after the CV screening phase will be contacted.
# The position is in Cluj-Napoca, but we also recruit candidates from outside Cluj-Napoca who are willing to relocate.






